OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers continuing overnight with some
OL,7,Fclearer spells in between. Showers
OL,8,Fbecoming more organised and heavier
OL,9,Flater during the early hours. Turning
OL,10,Fchilly in the countryside but mainly
OL,11,Ffrost-free.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,14,Fscattered showers, with some heavier
OL,15,Fshowers possible. Cloud building later
OL,16,Fwith some wet and windy weather
OL,17,Farriving by evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
