OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRain
OL,6,Fclearing Tuesday to a mix of sunshine
OL,7,Fand blustery showers. Further showers
OL,8,Fpossible on Wednesday, then turning
OL,9,Fdrier, brighter and warmer on Thursday.
